    <item>
      <title>花旗告诉私人银行家不要在中国大陆讨论人民币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/citi-tells-private-bankers-not-to-discuss-the-yuan-on-mainland</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，花旗集团告诉为中国客户提供服务的私人银行家，在前往内地时不要讨论人民币或对冲货币风险，这突显了在岸交易的敏感性日益增强。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/citi-tells-private-bankers-not-to-discuss-the-yuan-on-mainland</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 05:17:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度银行业 210 亿美元的溃败预示着最好的日子可能已经结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/a-21-billion-rout-in-india-s-banks-signal-best-days-maybe-over</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在印度最大的私营银行 HDFC Bank Ltd. 罕见遭到抛售后，价值 4,330 亿美元的印度银行业前景迅速恶化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/a-21-billion-rout-in-india-s-banks-signal-best-days-maybe-over</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 05:01:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经济学家表示，欧洲央行将选择首次降息的最佳时机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/ecb-to-pick-right-moment-for-first-rate-cut-economists-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析师表示，欧洲央行将成功判断何时开始降息，以在不破坏经济的情况下抑制通胀。分析师预计首次降息将在六月份进行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/ecb-to-pick-right-moment-for-first-rate-cut-economists-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲新兴市场股票将出现 2022 年以来最大单周资金流出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/em-asia-stocks-set-to-see-biggest-weekly-outflows-since-2022</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储大幅降息的希望减弱，削弱了风险资产的情绪，除中国外的亚洲新兴股市预计将出现 2022 年 6 月以来最大规模的单周资金流出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/em-asia-stocks-set-to-see-biggest-weekly-outflows-since-2022</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 03:51:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受中东动荡影响，油价稳定在今年最高收盘价附近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-19</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东紧张局势升级，油价收于三周高位后保持稳定，美国和伊朗支持的胡塞武装针锋相对的袭击扰乱了全球航运业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-19</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 23:53:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台积电上涨，亚洲股市和纳斯达克期货上涨：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于台积电的前景激发了人们对该行业全球复苏的希望，亚洲股市与纳斯达克 100 指数期货一起上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 22:21:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>达斯称印度央行尚未讨论降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/india-central-bank-not-discussing-rate-cuts-yet-governor-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行行长 Shaktikanta Das 表示，除非通胀稳定在 4% 目标附近，否则印度央行不会考虑降息，而政策制定者甚至还没有讨论这个话题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/india-central-bank-not-discussing-rate-cuts-yet-governor-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 11:07:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
